author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Watching all archive today and the stamps that fellow fandeads left on their comments, this delivery will be considered as the best... :_サイリウム碧: :_サイリウム紫:

Let's see... Various Fans and Followers found Rushia thanks to various events like, Broken Wii power cable, her scream at first FallGuys stream, her Rage gaming (Now not recommended due to health conditions about low pressure), the "Go Home" which for good or bad predicted the pandemic, her longest Superchat reading after normal deliveries... But mostly her pretty voice at singing, her healing ASMR streams and also her few times at cooking (Like Morning Activities and the Halloween Cooking event)... Wow, and her first 3D delivery, when danced, moved a lot and also kissed to audience...
About kissing the audience, she left that for a while, but at 2020 September 6th until now, that kissing habit returned to stay already there.

Sincerely, she deserves all love from us... Thank you, Rushia-daitenshi... We Love You:_ハート::_るんるん::_ちょうちょ:

author: aqamelon02
text:
Celebrating with a wonderful countdown Stream. Happy Birthday Rushia. 
0:00 Opening Graphics
* 1st year since the opening graphics debuted.
0:57 Intro talk
* Mostly talks about the yesterdays collab.
4:10 Start Fireworks Challenge (Until before 12:00 A.M)
11:49 Rushia does the Minecraft Cat Sound
27:10 Rushia tries to change BGM. 
27:15 Waiting for 12:00 a.m.
27:34 It's 12:00 a.m. HAPPY BIRTHDAY. Big SuperChat flow.
27:46 Firework Show Starts
29:37 Announcement for tomorrow's program.
* 29:45 Talk-part screen (SuperChat Orei Time text and "Thank you time" logo) shows by error. At 29:48 returns to gameplay, with only Piyoko flying.
33:42 Ollie Appears in Minecraft
46:26 English Cute Moment
47:31 Calling Ollie
50:56 Sleep Toghether
56:21 Very cute Rushia and Ollie moment. At 57:59 leaves Piyoko flying as Rushia does Height Comparison.
* 58:59 Rushia shows some additional Live2D capabilities (New Live2D designed by Tou-Illie)
1:05:48 Talk Part
1:13:00 SuperChat Orei Time
* 2:34:16 Nyanko messes the Microphone

Some Cute Laughs: 3:08, 3:18, 20:30, 37:46

Final Message: "Thank you very very much. Thank you!. Tomorrow, see you then everyone. Good Night. I have a lot of things to do. I'm Leaving"  (2:41:12, Rough ear translation)

author: Nexcell Pride
text:
A note about the height comparison... 
At 0:59:00 until 0:59:19 Rushia's model moved entirely like her New Live2D premiered at 2020 June 16th.

So, that current green haired form Live2D is her Live2D 2.0 modeled also by Tou Ilie and premiered at late February 2020 (Private video)

Tou Ilie also made the New Year's kimono model at Early January 2020.

It's notorious because being based on Yasuyuki-sensei's original concept, Tou Ilie model's factions are like as first Yasuyuki-sensei's vtuber creation: Kamiki Kinu (A short lived vtuber, also PLIVyou's founder member, debuted at 2018 October 2nd and graduated at 2019 May 31st)
